description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '20-min BODYWEIGHT Full Body Workout | [Build Muscle & Strength]' from the channel MrandMrsMuscle.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow-along and crush this 20 min bodyweight full body workout! This training session helps to build muscle and strength using compound movements and a moderate tempo per rep it also has an element of cardio and core moves that will ramp up calorie burn. We target the whole body with this workout including your legs (hamstrings, quadriceps and calves), glutes (glute minimus, glute medius and gluteus Maximus) your chest, arms (shoulders, biceps and triceps), back and core (abs). Burn some body fat, expend calories and build your muscle in just 20 minutes full body strength workout.
